pageContext.claim: “Comey -- who, by the way, lied and leaked, and also leaked classified information.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence former FBI director James Comey leaked classified information. The only memo that Comey shared with the media, concerning Trump's request that Comey drop the Michael Flynn investigation, was not classified. He shared three other memos with an attorney, but is said to have redacted any secret or classified material.
